                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I don't agree. I view addControllerDirectory() in a similar light as the include_path, where precedence occurs left to right (i.e., FIFO); reversing the order seems counterintuitve.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
